Gold!

46
00:01:46,509 --> 00:01:47,969
You hear me?!

47
00:01:47,969 --> 00:01:48,969
Recycling other people’s garbage

48
00:01:48,969 --> 00:01:52,040
is a global industry worth billions.

49
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,740
And China is a huge part of it.

50
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:56,329
In 2016,

51
00:01:56,329 --> 00:01:59,749
China imported 45 million tonnes of scrap
metal,

52
00:01:59,749 --> 00:02:01,369
waste paper and plastic,

53
00:02:01,369 --> 00:02:05,139
together worth over 18 billion dollars.

54
00:02:05,139 --> 00:02:06,450
And it’s the United States

55
00:02:06,450 --> 00:02:09,630
that’s sending China most of its garbage.

56
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:13,159
According to the Solid Waste Association of
North America—

57
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,870
yes that’s a thing—

58
