98
00:03:49,819 --> 00:03:51,140
for six months,

99
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:53,769
while using recycled material to produce plastic

100
00:03:53,769 --> 00:03:55,440
reduces the energy required

101
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:59,030
by as much as 87 percent.”

102
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:01,139
So since China has benefitted so much

103
00:04:01,139 --> 00:04:03,560
