123
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:43,160
1.4 million tons of garbage a day.

124
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:45,870
Twice as much as the United States.

125
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:48,080
Half of that will be burned.

126
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:50,420
And according to an in-depth report by NPR,

127
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:53,900
