134
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,280
According to this study,

135
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:14,340
40,000 American jobs relied on

136
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:16,530
the garbage and recycling industry.

137
00:05:16,530 --> 00:05:17,530
And in China,

138
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:20,120
